title: This Teenager Discovered Her Doppelgänger. And Then Another. And Then Another. And Then Another.
text: Back in September, a 17-year-old California college student named Santana Gutierrez met her doppelgänger, Isobel, in a mall. The pair met when Isobel approached Gutierrez to discuss the Save the Children fund. “I kind of felt bad ’cause I wasn’t listening to what she was saying — all I was... More »
